text:
Was looking for Curry Chee Cheong Fun in the area and found this place.
Inside Koufu foodcourt.
I had curry Chee cheong fun with roast meat ($5)

Taste wise, soso only.
Roast meat is ok.
Curry not hot.
Portion is good for a afternoon snack.
Excellent ipoh curry chee cheong fun with pig skin, crispy roast pork & fragrant ipoh curry mee
